b4a2160b6cc72c91","tid":1929090,"uid":63843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T18:28:30.000Z","msg":"照直講囉 怕咩<br />\n就算真係唔借咪出去搵炒散<br />\n肯搵炒散就一定有<br />\n炒散都唔肯搵又要先洗未來錢就食撚屎"},{"pid":"f57ce731359ec54587607a28ed4ef4672900b1eb","tid":1929090,"uid":247184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T18:36:04.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾"},{"pid":"a1bbd7ffad7c29448906b19911f4f68e2341aa7b","tid":1929090,"uid":335283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f57ce731359ec54587607a28ed4ef4672900b1eb","tid":1929090,"uid":247184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T18:36:04.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T18:38:31.000Z","msg":"咪係"},{"pid":"66fbc3f44fac902e1405b76a3cf7cbfb390ecfe9","tid":1929090,"uid":202011,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T19:08:33.000Z","msg":"點解可以完全唔儲錢 賺幾多洗曬幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全唔諗有意外 咁樣邊得㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你本來兩萬蚊都冇 就學人碌兩萬蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n借兩萬都要諗 即係本來屋企應該都唔富貴啦(?)<br />\n<br />\n市道差都唔係呢一兩個月嘅事<br />\n覺得自己可以穩定工作？<br />\n唔有錢就咁大洗  諗嘢又唔防範於未然<br />\n你呢啲人唔肯改 有嘢就搵屋企人<br />\n就正如樓上咁講 你係垃圾<br />\n<br />\n真心肯改嘅話 都支持你問屋企人借<br />\n理由就係「我知錯了」個啲囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n關係唔差始終會幫你嘅 <br />\n比啲行動力證明比屋企人睇<br />\n快啲搵抄散還錢比屋企人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油"}]}